  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Calculate Your CRO ROI in 30 Seconds</h1>
    <p class="sub">Enter your ad spend, conversion rate, and AOV — see your current ROAS and how a <strong>+20% CR</strong> boost impacts revenue.</p>

    <div class="card" id="calc">
      <div>
        <h3>See your CRO impact in seconds</h3>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="adSpend">Monthly Ad Spend (₹)</label>
            <input id="adSpend" type="number" min="1000" step="500" value="50000" />
            <div class="hint">Example: 50000</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="aov">Average Order Value (₹)</label>
            <input id="aov" type="number" min="100" step="50" value="1500" />
            <div class="hint">Example: 1500</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="cr">Current Conversion Rate (%)</label>
          <input id="cr" type="range" min="0.1" max="10" step="0.1" value="2.0" />
          <div class="hint">Current: <span id="crVal">2.0%</span></div>
        </div>

        <p class="disclaimer">This is a directional estimate. Actual results vary by traffic quality, offer, and UX.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="results">
